                        <span class="text-[#A50020] text-[8px]">◆</span> Connect</h4>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 font-sans text-base font-light text-[#4A4744]"><a href="#" class="hover:text-[#A50020] uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors w-fit flex items-center gap-2"><iconify-icon icon="solar:phone-linear"></iconify-icon> WhatsApp Direct</a><a href="mailto:engineering@hydradynamics.com" class="hover:text-[#A50020] tracking-widest transition-colors w-fit flex items-center gap-2"><iconify-icon icon="solar:letter-linear"></iconify-icon> engineering@hydradynamics.com</a></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:ml-auto">
                    <h4 class="uppercase text-xs font-medium text-[#1A1A1A] tracking-[0.25em] font-sans flex items-center gap-2">
